### Example 04 — move-to-service (OData source → OData target)

### Source: LogisticsService.Shipments
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$top=3

### Target: LogisticsService.ShipmentArchive (empty at start)
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/ShipmentArchive?$top=3

### Pipeline registered?
GET http://localhost:4104/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'ShipmentArchive'
